page.title: 15Stephanie's School Day
page.content: Tuesday I get up at about 7.55.I go down stairs,have my breakfast and clean my teeth,then I have a wash and get dressed for school.By the time I've done that and brushed my hair it is time to catch the school bus.We get to school at about 9.00.When we get into class we read our books while the teacher calls the register. Then we do some Maths or English. At 10.30 we go swimming at Witney swimming pool and we come back at 11.30.When we get back we carry on with our work until 12.10 then we go out to play until 1.15. In the afternoon we do topic and at 3.15 we go home. When I get home I watch T.V and have my tea at about 5.00.Then I go to see my nan and I come back at about 8.00. Sometimes I read a book and I go to bed at about 9.00.
